title: HAPPY 50TH BIRTHDAY QUESTLOVE!
itunes:title: HAPPY 50TH BIRTHDAY QUESTLOVE!
description:
Happy 50th birthday Questlove! In this VERY special episode, listen as hosting duties are taken away from our uber talented leader so that Team Supreme may pay the proper tribute to a man who has given so much to so many. We also invited some of those folks to tell their favorite Ahmir bka Questlove stories. Some voices you may recognize (-; Ladies and Gentlemen this is your Questlove Supreme episode celebrating the FIRST 50 years of Questlove!
